<h5>Governor Ned Lamont</h5>
<a href="/Office-of-the-Governor"></a><a href="/Office-of-the-Governor"><img alt="Headshot of Governor Ned Lamont" src="/-/media/Office-of-the-Governor/govlamont.jpg?h=140&amp;w=140&amp;sc_lang=en&amp;hash=223CAAE4F4A64AA05370BEB5C8D5F9B1" style="height: 140px; width: 140px;" /></a>
<p>
Together, we will revitalize Connecticut&rsquo;s economy to bring opportunity and prosperity to every one of our communities.&nbsp;</p>
</div>
<div class="officer">
<a href="/Wyman-Archive" title=" Landing Page for the Lt. Governor">
</a>
<h5>Lt. Governor Susan Bysiewicz</h5>
<a href="/Office-of-the-Lt-Governor"><img alt="Lt. Governor Bysiewicz" src="/-/media/Connecticut-Interactive/Main-Portal/ltgovbysiewicz-sm.jpg?h=140&amp;w=140&amp;sc_lang=en&amp;hash=2172CD6ED73414D89D3997C7E3618160" style="height: 140px; width: 140px;" /></a>
<p>
We are committed to equal pay, good-paying jobs, excellent public schools in every neighborhood, and an environment that nurtures entrepreneurship and shares its rewards.&nbsp;</p>
